properties.areaDesc: Great Salt Lake Desert and Mountains
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 6 at 8:37PM MST until February 7 at 9:00AM MST by NWS Salt Lake City UT
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 55 mph.

* WHERE...The Box Elder county portion of the Great Salt Lake
Desert and Mountains.

* WHEN...Until 9 AM MST Friday.

* IMPACTS...High profile and light weight vehicles will be
impacted by the strong and gusty winds along I-84 and State
Route 30 near the Idaho border. Areas of blowing and drifting
snow can be expected.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM MST FRIDAY
